Package View.Views.Admin

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PanelAdmin
    This Panel contains a tabbed pane that represents all the different functionalitites of the administrator.
    PanelAdminProjects
    This Panel contains the different functionalities of the administrator regarding projects (accept, denied, look more information...)
    PanelAdminSettings
    This Panel allows the admin to set the threshold and set the date
    PanelAdminUsers
    This Panel allows the admin to Accept, Reject, Ban and Unban users
